etos are a PRIVATE vote, do not expect to be told who/why/ a veto was posted. If that person wishes to discuss the issue with you, they will contact you and do so.<br><br><b>   +</b> If your application is declined due to insufficient votes, you are welcome to reapply after you have met more members. This includes both Trial and Full member areas of voting. Applications are valid for a period of 30 days, at that time if there are not enough votes, they will be closed.<br><br><b>   +</b> Real-Life significant others of full members are typically exempt from these rules.  Ask your local officer :)     Real-Life friends of full members will still need to apply, but the level limit will not be applied to them.<br><br>If you have any questions, please feel free to post them with your application or contact an officer in-game.<br><br><br><b><u>Application Questions</u></b><br><br>Applicant (Name, Level and Class) <br><br>Alts (Names, Levels and Classes) <br><br>Who is sponsoring your application to Aquilo di Arcis? <br><br>What made you decide to apply? <br><br>What guilds were you in previously? Why did you leave? <br><br>What does a guild mean to you? <br><br>What do you expect from being a member of Aquilo di Arcis? <br><br>What time zone do you live in? <br><br>Aquilo di Arcis is currently siding with Dragon faction, are you prepared to join this faction? <br><br>List some Aquilo di Arcis members you have grouped with and describe some of the things the group was up to at the time. <br><br>Have you had any negative experiences with any of our members? Explain. <br><br>Do you have any trade skills? <br><br>What is the one item you want most right now? <br><br>List some of the keys you have. (Ex: Howling Stones, Veshan's Peak, Cobalt Scar tooth) <br><br>How do you feel about twinking? <br><br>Where do you normaly hunt? <br><br>List some of your closest EQ friends. <br><br>List some of your EQ enemies. <br><br>Describe yourself in one word. <br><br>Give us a little history on your main character's life so far. <br><br>On a big hunt with a group you loot a monster and find it has a great item no one was expecting. What do you do? <br><br>You are hunting with your group in a dangerous area. A pull goes bad and the group is suddenly swarmed by mobs. You battle it out for a little while and suddenly the healer dies. With no healer left the person you were counting on to possibly evac you out is now laying dead on the floor as well. You have a near full health bar and your tanks are taking a beating.  What do you do? <br><br>You come across a game bug that benefits players greatly. What do you do? <br><br>You log into the game and cannot find anyone your level to group with. What do you do? <br><br><br>Cheers!<br>-Sulien <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub47.ezboard.com/uqudelle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qudelle</A> at: 1/22/02 7:50:30 am<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub47.ezboard.com/faquiloarcisfrm11.emailToFriend?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub47.ezboard.com/faquiloarcisfrm11.threadControl?topicID=8.topic><img src=http://www.dndwebdesign.com/Dawn/locked.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub47.ezboard.com/faquiloarcisfrm11.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub47.ezboard.com/faquiloarcisfrm11.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=8.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td c